e":47,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:16:38.000Z","msg":"只要中到手就吹得啦<br />\n唔關有無意圖事喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:21:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.livestrong.com/article/123838-fifa-soccer-rules-handball/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livestrong.com%2Farticle%2F123838-fifa-soccer-rules-handball%2F&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=d2995b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.livestrong.com/article/123838-fifa-soccer-rules-handball/</a><br />\n<br />\nNot Awardable<br />\nA handball should not be awarded if a player is ruled to have handled the ball accidentally. This refers to a player either attempting to protect himself from injury, for example by placing the hands in front of the face and then being hit by the ball, or a player being hit on the arm by the ball without moving towards the ball and without being able to move out of the way. An example might be a snap shot hitting the arm of a defender at point-blank range. However, if a player&rsquo;s arm is in an unnatural position, for example outstretched or above their head, then a foul should be awarded whether accidental or not.<br />\n<br />\n不過下年會改例，進攻球員有冇意圖只要一掂到手就會foul"},{"pid":"9694662fca91c6d4e8ef68e199f451bd550e6572","tid":1113272,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:24:58.000Z","msg":"都已成事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8d7752145a5363041ab63f89bdeca6ced73d53","tid":1113272,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:25:11.000Z","msg":"驗眼撚應該無咁快醒 去訓陣先"},{"pid":"11085713d7b9a153e399e810454f0f9dbce32e75","tid":1113272,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9694662fca91c6d4e8ef68e199f451bd550e6572","tid":1113272,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T22:24:58.000Z","msg":"都已成事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB